productReviews.reviewText: The box this comes in is 5 light-year by 6 foot and weights 17 megaton!!!
My macaroni penguin loves to play with it.
My co-worker Cato has one of these. He says it looks sopping.
It only works when I'm Wake Island.
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
